PLUGIN-MIG-2 (Phase 16) 시점에 src/lib/aggregator/{rss,html,api,dedupe,classify,llm,promote,cleanup,runner}.ts 본체를 이 디렉토리로 이전.

이전 단위:
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/rss-fetcher.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/fetchers/rss.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/html-scraper.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/fetchers/html.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/api-poller.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/fetchers/api.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/classifier.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/{classify,llm}.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/promoter.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/promote.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/handlers/cleanup.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/cleanup.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/lib/dedupe.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/dedupe.ts
- packages/tenant-almanac/src/types.ts ← src/lib/aggregator/types.ts (RawItem / EnrichedItem)

각 핸들러는 TenantCronHandler 시그니처 — packages/core 의 dispatchTenantJob 가 호출.
